<p>A magnitude 5.5–5.7 earthquake struck central Bangladesh near Narsingdi, east of Dhaka, on Friday, killing at least five people and injuring many. Reported figures vary across outlets, from roughly 100 injured and five to seven dead to over 300–350 injured and nine to ten dead, as assessments continue [dawn.com#1][scmp.com#1][thehindu.com#1][abcnews.go.com#1][ndtv.com#1][aljazeera.com#1][aa.com.tr#1][aljazeera.com#3]. The epicentre was reported around Narsingdi, about 30–40 km from Dhaka [dawn.com#1][bbc.com#1]. Buildings in Dhaka swayed, residents rushed into the streets, and tremors were felt in parts of eastern India, with no immediate reports of major damage there [dawn.com#1][thehindu.com#1][scmp.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/YYWbKa9YFgqp86aXOEcPNWo3NlNgjU7c8kRlCCmpNAKhxZ0E8nAgVFEUL66Q7tPNVWxzVz3Ux8cyjqRVhgXikVrEQKLXYEB4IRcDGG7yw5pa' alt='Security personnel stand near rubble from a damaged building in Old Dhaka after the earthquake on November 21, 2025.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Epicentre: Initial reports placed the epicentre in Narsingdi, roughly 30–40 km east of Dhaka [dawn.com#1][bbc.com#1].</li><li>Casualties: Reported fatalities range from at least five up to ten, with injuries ranging from around 100 to more than 350 as tallies evolve [aljazeera.com#3][scmp.com#1][thehindu.com#1][abcnews.go.com#1][ndtv.com#1][aljazeera.com#1][aa.com.tr#1][dawn.com#1].</li><li>Notable victims: Two children were among the dead, the government said [scmp.com#1].</li><li>Structural impacts: Police reported three deaths when a railing of a six‑storey building collapsed during the quake; debris from buildings under construction also injured people [dawn.com#1].</li><li>Government response: Authorities said they are closely monitoring the situation and directed departments to intensify rescue operations; the injured include Dhaka University students, factory workers in Gazipur, and residents of Narsingdi [dawn.com#1].</li></ul><blockquote>We felt a strong jolt and buildings were shaking like trees. Staircases were jammed as people rushed down. Everyone was terrified, children were crying. - Suman Rahman, Dhaka resident</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Bangladesh interim government: Officials said the government is closely monitoring the situation and ordered intensified rescue operations; injured include students, factory workers, and Narsingdi residents [dawn.com#1]. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956489/earthquake-jolts-bangladesh-killing-five-and-injuring-around-100'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Dhaka residents: Residents described strong shaking that sent people rushing down staircases and into the streets [dawn.com#1]. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956489/earthquake-jolts-bangladesh-killing-five-and-injuring-around-100'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Indian authorities: Tremors were felt in bordering eastern states and Kolkata, with no immediate reports of major damage in India [dawn.com#1][thehindu.com#1][scmp.com#1]. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956489/earthquake-jolts-bangladesh-killing-five-and-injuring-around-100'>Dawn; The Hindu; SCMP</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/9-dead-over-300-injured-in-bangladesh-after-5-5-magnitude-earthquake-9678819#publisher=newsstand'>9 Dead, Over 300 Injured In Bangladesh After 5.5-Magnitude Earthquake</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/south-asia/article/3333750/2-children-among-dead-bangladesh-rattled-magnitude-57-earthquake'>2 children among dead as Bangladesh rattled by magnitude 5.7 earthquake</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/11/21/deadly-earthquake-shocks-bangladesh-hundreds-injured'>Deadly earthquake shocks Bangladesh, hundreds injured</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/earthquake-magnitude-57-strikes-bangladesh-november-21-2025/article70306240.ece'>Bangladesh earthquake of magnitude 5.7 kills six, injures dozens</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cvgke7e2jx8o'>At least five killed in Bangladesh earthquake</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956489/earthquake-jolts-bangladesh-killing-five-and-injuring-around-100'>Earthquake jolts Bangladesh, killing five and injuring around 100</a> - dawn.com</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/55-magnitude-earthquake-central-bangladesh-kills-6-people-127739930'>A 5.5 magnitude earthquake in central Bangladesh kills at least 6 people</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aa.com.tr/en/asia-pacific/-57-magnitude-earthquake-kills-10-in-bangladesh/3749773'>A Mw 5.5 earthquake strikes central Bangladesh, killing ten people and wounding over 350 more. (AA)</a> - aa.com.tr</li></ul>